Theme

my_theme <- function(){
  list(
      theme_minimal(),
      scale_fill_manual(values=c("#A46583", "#e05d00", "#89A46F", "#7FBDFF"), 
                       name="Leagues",
                       breaks=c("MLB", "NBA", "NFL", "NHL"),
                       labels=c("MLB", "NBA", "NFL", "NHL"))
    )
}
G_theme <- function(){
  list(
      theme_minimal(),
      scale_fill_manual(values=c("#AA1E23", "#F03C4B", "#FB8987", "#FAC8C8"), 
                       name="Leagues",
                       breaks=c("MLB", "NBA", "NFL", "NHL"),
                       labels=c("MLB", "NBA", "NFL", "NHL"))
    )
}
